data.text: Dear bloggers, The minister to the state of Kerala for Urban development and Minority Welfares,I have immense pleasure to bring before you my blog "manjalamkuzhi.blogspot.in". We live in an age which the state-of-the-art technology are advancing very fast and they become a major tools of communication. By publishing this blog my aim is to interact my personal outlooks on politics, arts and various social issues with you. Besides, you can also keep in touch with me via facebook and twitter.
